      "span_text": "The studies should compare two or three surgery instruments (SPLC, 2PLC, 3PLC, 4PLC, and mini-4PLC). SPLC was defined as laparoscopic excision of the gallbladder performed through a single abdominal incision using either a multiport device or different individual ports through the same single skin incision [CITATION_1] ."
